       \"text\": \"Comparing current state vs. last known DTLX baseline (22:55 UTC report):\\n\\n| Session | Last Report | Current | Δ |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX monitor) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — (normal cycle) |\\n| `telegram:group:-5163901258` | done ✅ | done ✅ | — |\\n\\nAll sessions stable. No new failures. No blockers.\\n\\n**Silent — no report.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 30714,\n            \"output\": 517,\n            \"totalTokens\": 45605,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 430,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776211767226,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e0a38f2874317bad3bb95471fa65d\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"1489eb4e\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776211449191,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 55909,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776162044660,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776162158012,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 113352,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-o