a specific message to a Telegram group. Let me check if there's a way to send Telegram messages through the available tools.\n\nLooking at the tools available, I don't see a direct Telegram sending tool. The tools available are:\n- read, edit, write, exec\n- process\n- sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_spawn, sessions_yield\n- subagents\n- web_search, web_fetch\n- image\n- browser\n- memory_search, memory_get\n- Various confluence tools\n- Various gitlab tools\n- Various stitch tools\n- tts\n\nThere's no direct Telegram message tool. I should reply with the CANNOT_SEND format as instructed."},{"type":"text","text":"CANNOT_SEND: No Telegram messaging tool available in current toolset. Available tools do not include a Telegram send/post function."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":379,"output":172,"totalTokens":11577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":11026,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776187812251,"responseId":"062daca5eb38f6849339f9f4c9083b45","__openclaw":{"id":"7b8fc739","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","label":"telegram-5p-status-v5","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-planner-subagent-63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776185050306,"sessionId":"0ca2d212-43d7-42cb-a3eb-01e64cd33376","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11258,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776184755002,"endedAt":1776184856849,"runtimeMs":11708,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/planner/sessions/0ca2d212-43d7-42cb-a3eb-01e64cd33376.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task is to send a specific message to a Telegram group. I need to use the `message` tool to send this message to the Telegram channel. Let me check the available tools... \n\nLooking at the tools, I don't see a direct `message` tool. But I see there's a `tts` (text-to-speech) tool. However, that won't send a Telegram message.\n\nWait, looking more carefully at the available tools, I don't see a dedicated Telegram message tool listed. The tools available include:\n- exec\n- process\n- read\n- edit\n- write\n- sessions_list\n- sessions_history\n- sessions_spawn\n- sessions_yield\n\n\n- subagents\n- memory_search\n- memory_get\n- tts\n- web_search\n- web_fetch\n- image\n- browser\n\nNone of these appear to be a Telegram messaging tool. Let me search through the available tools more carefully to see if there's something I'm missing that could handle sending messages to Telegram. I'm realizing I don't have access to a dedicated Telegram messaging tool in this environment—the available tools are primarily for browsing, file operations, and session management, none of which handle external messaging like Telegram. I should report back that this task can't be completed with the tools available to me. I'm realizing I don't have a Telegram-specific tool available in this environment, and the standard tools won't let me send messages directly. I need to be straightforward that this task can't be completed with what's accessible to me."},{"type":"text","text":"I don't have a Telegram messaging tool available in this environment. The available tools are: exec, process, read, edit, write, sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_spawn, sessions_yield, subagents, memory_search, memory_get, tts, web_search, web_fetch, image, browser, plus specialized MCP tools (stitch, confluence, gitlab).\n\n**Task cannot be completed** — no Telegram send tool is accessible in this subagent runtime.\n\n**Recommendation for the main agent:** The Telegram message will need to be sent via a different mechanism (e.g., a dedicated Telegram bot runner, a cron/macro that calls the Telegram API directly, or a parent agent with the appropriate tool)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":336,"output":448,"totalTokens":11706,"cacheRead":7447,"cacheWrite":3475,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184845234,"responseId":"062da10dffbe4344ad63a1cddfb9e551","__openclaw":{"id":"8eaf43c5","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776184692752,"sessionId":"2514861e-9ccc-41ee-8f48-1e19d13c0819","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11075,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776184464031,"endedAt":1776184688954,"runtimeMs":16394,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/2514861e-9ccc-41ee-8f48-1e19d13c0819.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The main Orbis session is acknowledging the failure and will send directly. This subagent task is complete."},{"type":"text","text":"Roger that. Task acknowledged — Telegram delivery handled by Orbis main session.\n\n**Subagent Status:** ✅ Complete (no further action needed)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":53,"totalTokens":11128,"cacheRead":7305,"cacheWrite":3770,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184684667,"responseId":"062da06d54b05398611ec226e7da423f","__openc